  "notes": "Route 44 is the penultimate Johto route, connecting Mahogany Town to Ice Path (and thus Blackthorn City). The route is wide and flat with two large central fishing ponds. The northern corridor is dominated by tall grass with mid-to-high-level Grass/Normal types. Trainers are spread across both sides of the ponds. Fisher Wilton and Bird Keeper Vance are rematching Pokegear contacts. The warp at (56,7) is the Ice Path entrance. pokecrystal object constants: ROUTE44_FISHER1=Wilton, ROUTE44_FISHER2=Edgar, ROUTE44_YOUNGSTER1=Psychic Phil (uses Youngster sprite reference in object_const_def, but the actual trainer class is PSYCHIC_T), ROUTE44_SUPER_NERD=Pokemaniac Zach, ROUTE44_YOUNGSTER2=Bird Keeper Vance, ROUTE44_COOLTRAINER_M=Allen, ROUTE44_COOLTRAINER_F=Cybil."
}